name: Dogon Galaxy
description: This is a gif I composited in the early 2000's.  The atom loop comes from an old nuclear documentary and the eye might be from it as well.  I colorized the eye using After Effects Colorama plugin. After combining the 2 I put it on top of an image of a Dogon tribesman and then put that composite on the image of the lake and Milky Way.  My first NFT!  1000x700 gif 8bit // 256 colors.
